        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for report [on echinoderms, <hi rend="italic">Ann. &amp; Mag. Nat. Hist.</hi> 2d ser. 8 (1851): 1–19]. Wanted to learn about metamorphosis of the class. Agrees with THH’s distinction between individuals and zooids, but thinks zooids will never cease to be called individuals.</p> 
        </abstract>
